title: Meadow Farm Foods
description: Health food store offering a complete selection of quality natural products and many organic products, with an emphasis on promoting foods from local sources. Inside the 3,500+ square foot store, you will find the basics: bread, coffee; a large selection of bulk foods with the Meadow Farm Food's private label, groceries, organic produce, spices, seasonal fruits, vitamins, herbs, natural personal care, essential oils, household cleaners, and books.
